    "author_type": "admin",
    "author_id": "admin-jmurray",
    "body": "On the hosted plan it's 120 requests/minute per token, and the response includes X-RateLimit-Remaining headers. Self-hosted has no limit by default but you can set API_RATE_LIMIT in your env.",
    "created_at": "2026-02-10T10:51:00.000Z"
